---

<section class="py-16 lg:py-20">
  <div class="max-w-[1440px] mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="relative rounded-[1.25rem] bg-mf-blue-deeper overflow-hidden px-8 py-12 lg:px-16 lg:py-14" data-animate>
      <!-- Decorative elements -->
      <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-64 h-64 bg-mf-green/[0.06] rounded-full -translate-y-1/2 translate-x-1/3"></div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-40 h-40 bg-white/[0.02] rounded-full translate-y-1/2 -translate-x-1/4"></div>

      <div class="relative flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-start lg:items-center justify-between gap-8">
        <div class="max-w-xl">
          <p class="text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-mf-green-light/70 mb-4">Oportunidades</p>
          <h2 class="font-[family-name:var(--font-display)] text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-extrabold text-white leading-[1.15] mb-3">
            Trabaje con nosotros
          </h2>
          <p class="text-white/50 text-sm lg:text-[15px] leading-relaxed">
            En Multiflex valoramos el talento y el compromiso. Si busca formar parte de un equipo profesional en crecimiento, nos encantaría conocerle. Envíenos su información y lo contactaremos.
          </p>
        </div>

        <a
          href="mailto:khenry@multiflexcr.com?subject=Interés en trabajar con Multiflex"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-mf-green hover:bg-mf-green-dark text-white font-medium rounded-full px-7 py-3.5 text-sm transition-colors shrink-0"
        >
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <rect x="2" y="4" width="20" height="16" rx="2" />
            <path d="M22 7l-10 6L2 7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" />
          </svg>
          Enviar mi información
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
